{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And actually, she got-- and such incidents were not rare.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then another thing, the hunger was so great, the majority of the food came in smuggled in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The people dug a hole under the fence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went out-- mostly children smuggled out-- out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they bought or-- or they went to some houses to get some food if they knew somebody or so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And on the way back, many of them got caught.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every day, there were dead children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Children, I mean 10, 12-year-old, even 8-year-olds that went out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] brought in whatever food they could to share with their family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And many of them got killed in such a way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But you die from starvation, so you die from a bullet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there wasn't much choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people that died, who got-- they collected them on-- on a wagon, and they took them to the Jewish cemetery and buried them in mass graves or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if there just was a few that particular day-- which was a rarity-- and they just allowed the very immediate family to follow, and then under the police supervision, bring them back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, [SCOFFS] they didn't even give that courtesy, they just took away the bodies, and who knows where.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Both life and death was very, very difficult in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, this was so ugly that people were holding on to life not to die in such an impersonal way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you know, you get shot, you get pulled by your hair and by your hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no respect for the living and no respect for the death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
